ter <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/girl-in-red-sabrina-carpenter-team-up-for-defiant-new-single-you-need-me-now-3608049">与 Girl In Red 合作发行了新单曲“You Need Me Now?”，</a>之后发布了这篇文章。 </p><figure id="attachment_3592195" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3592195" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3592195" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TaylorSwift-Sabrina-Carpenter-White-Horse-Coney-Island-collaborative-performance-Eras-Tour-news.jpg" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 和泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在悉尼一起在钢琴上表演，作为“Eras Tour”的一部分" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TaylorSwift-Sabrina-Carpenter-White-Horse-Coney-Island-collaborative-performance-Eras-Tour-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TaylorSwift-Sabrina-Carpenter-White-Horse-Coney-Island-collaborative-performance-Eras-Tour-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TaylorSwift-Sabrina-Carpenter-White-Horse-Coney-Island-collaborative-performance-Eras-Tour-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TaylorSwift-Sabrina-Carpenter-White-Horse-Coney-Island-collaborative-performance-Eras-Tour-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TaylorSwift-Sabrina-Carpenter-White-Horse-Coney-Island-collaborative-performance-Eras-Tour-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TaylorSwift-Sabrina-Carpenter-White-Horse-Coney-Island-collaborative-performance-Eras-Tour-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3592195" class="wp-caption-text">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 和泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在悉尼演出，作为“Eras 巡演”的一部分。图片来源：Don Arnold/TAS24/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 将于五月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-adds-two-new-london-eras-shows-with-paramore-3538573">恢复欧洲站的纪念性巡演</a>，以巴黎洛杉矶德芳斯体育馆 (LA Défense Arena) 的一场演出拉开序幕，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">帕拉莫尔</a>(Paramore) 将为她提供支持。与此同时，斯威夫特今年早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-album-the-tortured-poets-department-3582273">在格莱美颁奖典礼上</a>宣布了一张<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-final-variant-3595989">全新专辑《The Tortured Poets Department》</a>将于 4 月 19 日发行。</p><p> 3 月 14 日，斯威夫特正在进行的巡演的演唱会影片<em>《泰勒·斯威夫特：时代之旅》（泰勒版）</em>在 Disney+ 上发布。仅仅三天后，就宣布这部电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/taylor-swift-eras-tour-disney-most-streamed-music-film-3603951">打破了该平台有史以来播放量最多的音乐特别节目的记录</a>。这部时长三个半小时的电影是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-the-eras-tour-film-breaks-new-box-office-record-3511013">在 10 月份上映的原版电影的</a>基础上进行扩展的，其中收录了之前从原版版本中删除的歌曲，包括《羊毛衫》和《万岁》。</p><p>萨布丽娜<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-reflects-on-eras-tour-with-taylor-swift-what-a-whirlwind-3608849">·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 反思与泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的 Eras 巡演：“What a 旋风”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
